P_{U+V} (x)= (P_{U} * P_{V})(x)
P_{U}
P_{V}
P_{U}(x) = \mathcal{N}(\mu_{U},\sigma_{U}^{2})
P_{V}(x) = \mathcal{N}(\mu_{V},\sigma_{V}^{2})
P_{U+V} (x)= \mathcal{N}(\mu_{U} + \mu_{V},\sigma_{U}^{2}+\sigma_{V}^{2})
P_{U}
P_{V}
P_U=\mathcal N(M_U,C_U)
P_V=\mathcal N(M_V,C_V)
P_U\ast P_V=\mathcal N(M_U+M_V,C_U+C_V)
M
n\times 1
C
n\times n
